/swan/designs/filter/ get

get

Retrieves basic necessary info of designs filtered by provided category, section and quantity (if provided).

get /swan/designs/filter/

Retrieves basic necessary info of designs filtered by provided category, section and quantity (if provided).

  • Request
  • Response

Query Parameters

  • category: (string )

    category of the dresses to be returned

    Example:

    fashion
  • section: (string )

    section, within the category, of the dresses to be returned

    Example:

    evening
  • quantity: (string )

    amount of projects to be retrieved

    Example:

    4
  • last_id: (string )

    id of the design since which the requested amount should be retrieved.

    Example:

    1
  • sku: (string )

    sku of the design to be retrieved

    Example:

    w-123-123

HTTP status code 200

OK

Body

Type: application/json
